Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:59.76,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.15,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:08.20,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh，you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:13.79,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.03,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:19.82,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:27.05,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:30.53,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}We won't fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:38.46,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:44.22,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:47.75,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Calling you，so like a little child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:51.17,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.31,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wish I could see your insides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:57.38,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}My love，you've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.87,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.34,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You know what our lives would be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:11.75,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Oh，you are the one I believe
