Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（公共電話）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  火村學長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起離開這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕一秒  我也不想讓你再待在那裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自說自話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一個沒有那傢伙的地方  讓我們重新開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真強硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  既然你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨  久瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒過來就看見你們  我還是下地獄的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打119嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,000就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  不用叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才  我把和瑞希的關繫了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此分手  相信今後不會再見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像與前女友那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不激揚青春嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早就不是談青春的年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想了結我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果做過火的話  連回憶都會消失得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就沒有不捨得忘掉的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總還是有點快樂的經歷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經走得很遠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下面該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都沒計劃過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去填飽肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先逛逛房產中介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個住處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  不想吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說不吃午飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒理由要硬撐著不吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想出人頭地了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我而拋棄人生  可不會有什麼好處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做…你早晚會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經後悔過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會再後悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過吧  我是你的初戀情人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說過  初戀還持續著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:32.78,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆  叨擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.67,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來啊…好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  平時都是立即回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我喜歡你  這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這一點一直都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是謊言  是真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍著不眨眼  可真夠累人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.74,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強了  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連身份都說不清  誰會租房給我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說得還不夠清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是離家出走的學生兩名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份可疑的兩人這一點是夠清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼…找不到房子  今晚睡哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地缺乏計劃性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種突發狀況下  怎麼定計劃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今晚就找個旅館住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅館？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀學長  你剛才往不健康的方向想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰  誰想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說傻話也要有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那個…可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去旅館住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找到工作前  儲蓄必須得省著花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可住處要是定不下來  工作也無從談起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是基督徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不都是神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您今晚賜我們容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧是夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是冬天就凍死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的夜晚也很涼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣一來就暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就不是純潔之身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是優子這一點沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你變成什麼樣  我的心意也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始建20年前  四疊半的單間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.19,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：疊是日本特有面積單位，大小在1.6平方米左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚房衛生間一律共用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種條件  房租居然還比我之前租的地方貴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押金禮金全免  立刻可以入住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠那種應付差事的身份證明就能租房給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是萬幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專供有難言之隱人士的公寓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來必須得注意防盜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連手機都沒有的人  還有什麼東西怕被盜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節時買給她的紅色手錶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…你去世妹妹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯獨沒法丟棄它…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  寫生簿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用它來打發時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是你扔給我的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…因為這個你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在同情我  在可憐我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想要那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  優子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是因為那樣才跟你來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  優子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻…居然相信了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  你也只是把我當作自我滿足的道具不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感受  對你來說都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和明良兄長有什麼區別！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  也許你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和雨宮一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直在為沒能保護好茜而懊悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這不是同情  也不是什麼可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不是用你做茜的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  我只是想保護你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不會鬆開這雙手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:32.24,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}從天空中搖曳著飄落下一根白色羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦  夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還只是實習  沒正式工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯做好了  快趁熱吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈亮著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說  再怎麼寒酸的公寓裏也得有電燈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人住的時候  可沒有過回到家裏有燈亮著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家時有人在等著的感覺真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是回來晚了我就關燈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門鎖了睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哭著求情也不給你開門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  一定要早點回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君回家的地方  也是我回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  這裏也是我的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個累贅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君至今的所有努力都付之流水了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再努力不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我畫像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長人物畫…不過還是畫畫看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說和前女友分手的事時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她反倒替我哭了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我都沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼…現在的我特別想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有經歷過挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是因為我不會去做可能失敗的事而選擇逃避罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把我扔進這個無法逃避的遊戲里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要讓我去玩一場注定會輸的遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顆心臟…還有瑞希…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我這個沒有未來的人還能做什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底我還能再做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨  我明白你的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是在崩潰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的你們又能明白什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算你自暴自棄  也不會有什麼好結果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都死到臨頭了  還會有什麼好結果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就放棄的話  你什麼也得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想聽你教訓我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂得死心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒完沒了地繼續著已經結束的遊戲的傢伙又懂得什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不會再見到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不會再見到…雨宮優子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掙的錢夠餬口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可中途退學的你很難找工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來買包煙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想讓我把優子交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你能決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  也不是我能決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道優子會想回你那裏去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若沒有別的地方可回的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也只能這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是沒法做她的歸宿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是她的避難所  並不是真的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問原因  那是因為你自己也一直在逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒逃嗎  那個地震的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  你把唯一的妹妹給丟棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起  你就遠離爭鬥  只是不斷逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才會放開優子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又放棄了畫畫  放棄了顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避著我  逃避著曾經的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  你只是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說我還能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你自己也意識到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不小心了  買個像樣點的鎖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正能做的  就是在那場地震中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你妹妹一起死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一清二楚的  要問為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也曾想過要那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那一天我卻沒有在妹妹身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是十分羨慕你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時  又十分地恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  你和你妹妹是在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  你卻逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有去救你妹妹  而是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有去和你妹妹一起死掉  而是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.89,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明明是你重要的妹妹  而你卻逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在恐懼和痛苦中呼喚著你  而你卻逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以和她一起去死  而你卻逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明明是衷心期盼的命運  而你卻逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為她贖罪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你獲得她的寬恕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能坦然地去尋找幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  你還會再一次失去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己的歸宿都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要…失去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在逃嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…又在逃了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君  夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回來吧  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  火村學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪學長  你到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想青春一把嗎  這下滿足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「明明不會再見到雨宮優子了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不說出這句話  我死都不能瞑目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕  倒是你才不要老糾結著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久瀨  你知道有些話能說  有些話不能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  說來風也還糾結著那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好冷靜一下頭腦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  你會存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都有段時間沒做過夢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希  有你的東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是久瀨先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是送貨的人搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  住址寫的是這裏  收件人也是瑞希哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正壞掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:54.18,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是久瀨先生吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓海風弄潮小提琴可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候真的很受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風姐居然說自己是女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算硬讓兩人分開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心靈依舊相通  就沒辦法了結關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了結…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的時候  如果自己墜入情網就算輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要讓對方愛上自己才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是久瀨的口頭禪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然充滿久瀨先生的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是被你愛上了  可就要輸了的卻是久瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事…輸到體無完膚的是我才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭…好想哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙從來只打必勝之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他贏不了輸了還能再站起來的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠拯救那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料外的邂逅  讓心支離破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ef - a tale of melodies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,return
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到嗎？  ——那真實的旋律

